Alienware 17, 2013 model. 
It was an absolute high end top spec beast when I have purchased it. The 765m was very close to the top of the range 780m, which was a marvel of technology at that time. It was running every game at ultra details for a few good 4-6 years, in the 6th year I had to start adjusting settings. Needless to say, in its glory days, this laptop has brought many smiles and countless moments of joy and high-end entertainment to me and my close friends. I was really in love with the Alienware software, allowing me to change the colors and to customize in game behavior and customize themes and more. 
